1) To start a new service to expose our backend servise using a load Balancer.
kubectl expose deployment blockchain-org1peer1 --type=LoadBalancer --name=my-service --port 80 --target-port 8080


2) To delete the service
kubectl delete service my-service

3) Install vim in pod
apt-get update
apt-get install vim

4) Install node js in pod
apt-get install curl
curl -sL https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_9.x | bash
apt-get install nodejs

5) Install express js
npm install express
npm install shelljs
